es.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aAnti-racismzGreat Britain. 0aRacial justicezGreat BritainxLegal aspects. 7aLAW / General.2bisacsh1 aThomas KC, Leslie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2024z9783111299655oZDB-23-BUPP40uhttps://doi.org/10.56687/9781529230765?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781529230765423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781529230765/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-BUPPb2024